OL,5,G2335 Mission Killfast
OL,6,     FAn adrenalized thrill ride with a
OL,7,     Fhigh-kicking CIA agent, Vegas
OL,8,     Fgangsters, mad arms dealers,
OL,9,     Fnuclear terrorists, explosions,
OL,10,     Fand bikini-clad beauties.
OL,11,G0135 Stereo Underground
OL,12,     FRichard Latto presents alternative
OL,13,     Fanthems from a music community
OL,14,     Fwith attitude.
OL,15,G0235 Father Brown
OL,16,     FA wealthy Scottish advocate of
OL,17,     Ftemperance and atheism is found
OL,18,     Fwith a broken neck apparently
OL,19,     Fhaving fell from an upstairs
OL,20,     Fwindow on his estate.
